name: GULAG
description:
GULAGToken is a community driven DeFi project fair-launched on Binance Smart Chain in July 2021. We aim to give holders the power to govern major decisions regarding the token and its development. GULAG Token generates rewards to holders true tokenomics and static reflections. 
-11% of all transactions are redistributed to all holders.
- 4% of all transactions are injected into the liquidity pool which will enable an increasingly stable price floor.
